Inventory.

Use inventory to review what you are carrying and wearing.

Common forms:

inventory
  Show your inventory.

i
  Short alias for inventory.

look <item>
  Look more closely at something you are carrying.

wear <item>
  Wear armor or clothing, if the item can be worn.

wield <item>
  Wield a weapon, if the item can be wielded.

drop <item>
  Drop an item, if the item can be dropped.

Some special objects cannot be dropped, sold, or put into containers.
